Monty-Hall

Game Rules:
    There are 3 doors
        1 door has a prize
        2 doors have a goat
    Player selects 1 door
    Game reveals 1 door does not have what they need
    Player chooses to do:
        Swap Doors
        Stay
    Player wins/loses on reveal

Simulation:
    How many times to run the sim?
    Input a door selection
        Remove door from data structure
    rand choose to swap door or keep
    track win lose ratios

Test Driven:
    Advanced